   5156          /***************************************************************************//**
   5157           * @brief
   5158           *   Configure flash access wait states to support the given core clock
   5159           *   frequency and vscale level.
   5160           *
   5161           * @note Current implementation sets wait states depending on frequency only.
   5162           *   This assumes that applications running on Vscale enabled microcontrollers
   5163           *   never attemtps to set core frequency above 40MHz at VSCALE1 (1.0V).
   5164           *   Series 2 Config 1 devices does not support vscale.
   5165           *
   5166           * @param[in] coreFreq
   5167           *   The core clock frequency to configure flash wait-states.
   5168           *
   5169           * @param[in] vscale
   5170           *   Voltage Scale level. Supported levels are 0 and 1 where 0 is the default.
   5171           *   @li 0 = 1.1 V (VSCALE2)
   5172           *   @li 1 = 1.0 V (VSCALE1)
